About Jay
'I've been on the journalism faculty at NYU for more than 20 years. I have a PhD in media studies from NYU in 1986. Neil Postman was my teacher and chaired my dissertation. Whether I am writing, blogging, speaking, organizing stuff or just rabble rousing, my usual method is to make people deal with my ideas after listening carefully to the gaps, traps, oil slicks and dead spots in theirs.
